text: Ashutosh Agashe (born 21 October 1972) is an Indian cricket player and businessman. In his youth, he played the Ranji Trophy. He is currently managing director of Brihan Maharashtra Sugar Syndicate Ltd.. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Indian cricketers Category:Living people Category:Businesspeople from Pune Category:Marathi people
